My interests are in<UL>
  <LI>DNS protocols
      <UL>
         <LI>Protocol itself</LI>
         <LI>DNSSEC implementations
	   <UL>
	     <LI>I wrote <A HREF="dnssec/index.html">my private DNSSEC configuration memo (Japanese language)</A>.</LI>
	   </UL>
	 </LI>
         <LI>Multi DNS server problems on Japanese FLETS</LI>
      </UL>
  </LI>
  <LI>Simple Mail Transfer Protocol (SMTP)
      <UL>
         <LI>Email address internationalization</LI>
         <LI>DKIM</LI>
         <LI>another authentication</LI>
         <LI>SMTP over IPv6</LI>
      </UL>
  </LI>
  <LI>Internet protocol itself
      <UL>
         <LI>Lower layer protocols (vLan, PPPoE, ...)</LI>
         <LI>IPv6</LI>
         <LI>Multiple upper-link problems</LI>
      </UL>
  </LI>
  <LI>Operating systems
      <UL>
         <LI>FreeBSD</LI>
         <LI>NetBSD</LI>
	 <LI>...</LI>
      </UL>
  </LI>
  </UL>
