Software Distributions
<UL>
<LI>DNSSEC small tool
  <UL>
    <LI><A href="dnssec/dnsseczonetool">dnsseczonetool</A> <A HREF="https://github.com/kfujiwara/dnsseczonetool">dnsseczonetool on github</A>   small zone maintenance script which uses BIND 9.6, 9.7's dnssec tools or NLnetLabs' LDNS tools</LI>
  </UL>
</LI>
<LI>Pcap file parse tool
  <UL>
    <LI><A href="http://jprs.co.jp/lab/people/fujiwara/pcapparsec/pcapparsec-0.3.1.tar.bz2">pcapparsec-0.3.1.tar.bz2</A>PCAP analyze program written in C, presented at CENTR Tech26 as <A HREF="http://www.centr.org/system/files/agenda/attachment/tech26-fujiwara-measurement_of_jp_queries.pdf">A method for large PCAP file analysis and preliminary results of JP DNS query measurement</A>.</LI>
  </UL>
</LI>
<LI>DNS query replay tool
  <UL>
    <LI><A HREF="dns_replay/dns_replay.c">dns_replay.c</A>, DNS replay tool, No documentation</LI>
    <LI><A HREF="dns_replay/dns_replay2.c">dns_replay2.c</A>, DNS replay tool (record queries and responses), No documentation</LI>
    <LI><A HREF="dns_replay/ParseOutput">ParseOutput</A>, parses output of dns_replay2.c, No documentation</LI>
    <LI><A HREF="dns_replay/replayconv">replayconv</A>, Convert BIND 9 query log for dns_replay.c</LI>
    <LI><A HREF="dns_replay/replayanalyze">replayanalyze</A>, Parse dns_replay output</LI>
	<LI><A HREF="dns_replay/querytcp.c">querytcp.c</A> <A HREF="https://github.com/kfujiwara/querytcp">querytcp on github</A>, TCP version of DNS queryperf</LI>
  </UL>
</LI>
<LI>Detecting unknown query ID responses<BR>
    for BIND 8.4.7 <A HREF="files/bind-8.4.7-IDattackLogging-00.diff">bind-8.4.7-IDattackLogging-00.diff</A><BR>
    for BIND 9.3.2/9.3.3/9.4.0 <A HREF="files/bind-9.3.2-IDattackLogging-00.diff">bind-9.3.2-IDattackLogging-00.diff</A>
</LI>
<LI>Access control facility for internet services for IPv6 (tcp wrappers like)<BR>
  <Font Color="#ff0000">Don't use this program. I don't use this program now.</FONT>
  <UL>
    <LI><A href="files/tcpd-v6-0.01e-20000221.tar.gz">tcpd-v6-0.01e-20000221.tar.gz</a>  with english doc(poor)</LI>
    <LI><A href="files/tcpd-v6-0.1e-20000419.tar.gz">tcpd-v6-0.1e-20000419.tar.gz</a>  using addrinfo library, sockaddr_storage, and corespond to v4-mapped address</LI>
  </UL>
</LI>
<LI>qmail IPv6 patch
